title: GoTo’s Rebound Hinges on Shareholder Vote as Grab Merger Eyed
description: Shares of GoTo Group are seeing signs of new life ahead of a shareholders’ meeting that may help pave the way for its long-awaited merger with larger rival Grab Holdings Ltd.
